messages.text:
You should write, within this action:

'conditions': [
  ['branding=="Chrome"', {
    'inputs': ['../chrome/app/theme/google-chrome/BRANDING']
  }, {  # else: branding!="Chrome"
    'inputs': ['../chrome/app/theme/chrome/BRANDING']
  }],
],

and remove BRANDING from the "normal" inputs list.  The correct BRANDING file will be added to inputs depending on the state of the "branding" GYP variable.
